Refund and Returns Policy

At FestivalRaveGear.com, we are committed to ensuring your satisfaction with every purchase. Below, you will find details about our refund and returns process to provide you with a seamless experience.

Overview
Our refund and returns policy lasts 30 days. If more than 30 days have passed since your purchase, we, unfortunately, cannot offer a full refund or exchange.

To be eligible for a return:

The item must be unused and in its original condition.
It must be returned in the original packaging.
A valid receipt or proof of purchase is required.
Non-returnable items:

Perishable goods (e.g., food, flowers).
Intimate or sanitary items.
Hazardous materials or flammable liquids and gases.
Gift cards, downloadable software, or certain health and personal care items.
Refunds
Once your return is received and inspected, we will notify you via email of its status:

If approved, your refund will be processed, and the credit will be applied to your original method of payment within 5-10 business days.
Steps if you haven't received your refund:

Check your bank or credit card account.
Contact your credit card company; it may take additional time for processing.
Contact your bank, as processing times can vary.
For unresolved issues, please email us at support@festivalravegear.com.

Sale Items
Refunds apply to full-priced items only. Sale items are not eligible for refunds.

Exchanges
We replace items only if they are defective or damaged. To initiate an exchange for the same product, email us at info@festivalravegear.com, and ship your item to [physical address].

Gifts
If the item was marked as a gift during purchase and shipped directly to you, you’ll receive a gift credit for your return.
If the gift wasn’t marked as such, the refund will be issued to the gift giver.
Shipping Returns
To return your item, mail it to: [physical address].

Important Shipping Notes:

Customers are responsible for return shipping costs. These are non-refundable.
For high-value items, consider trackable shipping or purchasing insurance.
Processing times for exchanged products may vary depending on your location.

Need Assistance?
For questions regarding returns, refunds, or exchanges, feel free to reach out:

Email: info@festivalravegear.com or support@festivalravegear.com
Website: FestivalRaveGear.com